Who: SCOURGE, SCORPONOK, Tuscon, Nightshift
Location: Black Fortress Hall ways

As Tuscon and other talked on the Autobot frequencies, two predacons had the
time to observe the conversation. "Ahhh, look what we have here." Scourge
said deresivly, "The prey squabbles amonst themselves." Scourge chuckles
as he and Scorponok turn the corner.

"Yes." Scorpnok siad as he smiled, "Let us help them!"

Even as they stepped around the lights came back on and the Auto-guns came
back online and began to orient on Tuscon and Nightshift, and they all open
fire on the Autobot duo.

At the same time Hydras gets a signal from Scorponok, "We have them, Tuscon
and his ugly twin Nightshift." Scorponok chuckled at his own joke, the sound
of weapons fire could be heard in the background.

(TAG)

Preston
